# Master shape — ops/docs consolidation (Constitutional Map)

> The contract for the from-trd series. Every concern below has exactly one canonical
> owner doc; every other doc points to it by link and never restates it. Restating a
> rule outside its owner is a defect.
>
> Spec: `{{trd_path}}` ({{trd_language}}) · Requirements: {{uc_count}} · Mode: {{mode}}
> Ratified by: {{ratified_by}} on {{ratified_date}}

## Goal

One owner per concern, so every rule in the spec has a traceable home and staleness becomes structurally impossible.

## Constitutional Map

| Concern | Canonical owner | Everyone else |
|---|---|---|
| How we work (commit discipline, naming, shape→craft→critique, LOC thresholds, slash commands) | `{{posture_docs.workflow}}` | link only |
| How the system looks (services, ports, schemas, flows) | `{{posture_docs.architecture}}` | link only |
| Tech pinned + rationale (no version overrides in shapes) | `{{posture_docs.stack}}` | link only |
| Test posture (what's worth testing, mocking policy, coverage) | `{{posture_docs.testing}}` | link only |
| Engineering principles (abstraction, comments, error handling, what to refuse) | `{{posture_docs.principles}}` | link only |
| Read-order at session start | `{{posture_docs.workflow}}` §0 | link only |
| Project state (status / shapes-index / roadmap) | generated meta-docs | never hand-edited |
| Terminology glossary | `{{posture_docs.workflow}}` §Glossary | link only |
| Canonical design system | `{{posture_docs.design}}` | STACK / ARCHITECTURE refer only |
| Canonical shape catalog | `{{shape_filename_pattern}}` | phase-style shapes deprecated |

## PR series

Each row lands as one focused PR with its own sub-shape (`{{shape_dir}}/{{master_basename}}-prN.md`).

| PR | Scope | Owner doc(s) touched |
|---|---|---|
| PR-1 | Sync architecture with live code | `{{posture_docs.architecture}}` |
| PR-2 | Posture single-owner consolidation | `{{posture_docs.principles}}`, `{{posture_docs.workflow}}` |
| PR-3 | Shape catalog cleanup | shapes |
| PR-4 | Meta-docs generator | `tools/scripts/refresh-docs-status.mjs` |
| PR-5 | JIT extraction policy | `{{posture_docs.workflow}}` §Shape naming |
| PR-6 | Translation pass (optional) | all prose docs |

> Greenfield runs collapse PR-1/3/5 (no live code, no existing shape catalog) into the greenfield track; the owner table above is authored fresh rather than reconciled.

